title: 2013 Match des Champions
text: The 2013 <a href="Match%20des%20Champions%20%28basketball%29">Match des Champions</a> was the 8th edition of the annual <a href="super%20cup">super cup</a> game in French basketball. This year the reigning <a href="LNB%20Pro%20A">LNB Pro A</a> champions <a href="JSF%20Nanterre">JSF Nanterre</a> faced off against <a href="French%20Basketball%20Cup">French Cup</a> champions <a href="Paris-Levallois%20Basket">Paris-Levallois Basket</a>. The game was played in the <a href="Vend%C3%A9space">Vendéspace</a> in <a href="Mouilleron-le-Captif">Mouilleron-le-Captif</a>.
